    {
      "ldu_id": "CBE_Annual_Report_Part_1-p5-t1-1",
      "document_id": "CBE_Annual_Report_Part_1",
      "content": "VALUES - (Continued)\nIv) Empowerment\n\u00c2 We distinguish employees as valuable organizational resources.\n\u00c2 We promote delegation of duties and responsibilities.\n\u00c2 We maintain an atmosphere that inspires confidence and take ownership.\n\u00c2 We take responsibility, support each other and serve customers in a courteous and respectful\nmanner.\n\u00c2 We recognize our employees for their best achievements.\nV) Innovative Organization\n\u00c2 We go above and beyond to find solutions to stakeholder problems leveraging technology\nwhere possible.\n\u00c2 We anticipate and respond to internal and external changes through constant improvement\nand adjustment.\n\u00c2 We establish a culture that nurtures individual and group learning.\n\u00c2 We retain and disseminate tacit knowledge across the Bank.\nVi) Teamwork\n\u00c2 We respect one another and cooperate in our work.\n\u00c2 We recognize the importance of teamwork for our success.\n\u00c2 We collaborate and support one another to ensure process integration and minimize external\nbusiness challenges.\nVii) Respect for Diversity\n\u00c2 We are responsive to cultural, ethical, religious or other values of employees and customers.\n\u00c2 We value diversity of ideas and viewpoints of our employees.\n\u00c2 We foster an environment of inclusiveness, where all people, regardless of their sex, age,\nbelief, etc. can exercise their maximum potential.\n\u00c2 We are committed to address the needs of our customers, regardless of their sex, age,\neducation etc.\n\u00c2 We are committed to listening to one another and respond appropriately.\nViii) Corporate Citizenship\n\u00c2 We value the importance of our role in national development endeavours and stand up for\nthis commitment.\n\u00c2 We abide by the laws of Ethiopia and other countries in which we do business.\n\u00c2 We care about the society\u2019s welfare and the environment.\n\u00c2 We believe that the sustainability of our business depends on our ability to maintain and\nbuild public confidence.\niii",
